    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in great shape for its next adventure! It runs super smoothly and has been really well-loved, making it a perfect pick if you're looking for quality without the brand-new price tag. I've kept up with the essentials, so it's totally ready to hit the road whenever you are. Drop me a message if you have any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see this go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have! \u2728",
