    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example is mechanically sorted, with the critical subframe reinforcement and VANOS solenoid maintenance already addressed. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox shifts with precision, and the factory limited-slip differential ensures linear power delivery out of corners. Upgraded with Bilstein B12 dampers and refreshed control arm bushings for enhanced lateral stability. While the finish shows light patina from spirited use, the powertrain remains robust and the throttle response is telepathic. A turn-key performance machine for the discerning pilot.",
